### Classes (append-only)
kg:Player       rdfs:subClassOf dbo:SoccerPlayer .
kg:Team         rdfs:subClassOf dbo:SportsTeam .
kg:Club         rdfs:subClassOf dbo:SoccerClub .
kg:NationalTeam rdfs:subClassOf dbo:SportsTeam .
kg:Match        rdfs:subClassOf dbo:SoccerMatch .
kg:Stadium      rdfs:subClassOf dbo:Stadium .
kg:Country      rdfs:subClassOf dbo:Country .
kg:City         rdfs:subClassOf dbo:Place .

### Core properties
kg:playsFor         rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:team .
kg:primaryPosition  rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:position .
kg:birthDate        rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:birthDate .
kg:shirtNumber      rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:number .
kg:homeTeam         rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:homeTeam .
kg:awayTeam         rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:awayTeam .
kg:venue            rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:location .
kg:kickoffTime      rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:time .

### Extra properties used by shapes
kg:nationality  rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:nationality .
kg:height       rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:height .
kg:weight       rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:weight .
kg:foundedDate  rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:foundingDate .
kg:homeStadium  rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:ground .
kg:locatedIn    rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:location .
kg:capacity     rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:capacity .
kg:attendance   rdfs:subPropertyOf dbo:attendance .
